snippet.title: Super Mario Bros Mini Gameplay Preview
snippet.description:
Gameplay preview of a remake of SMB1 for the gameboy made with GBStudio.

You can download the game and the source code here:

https://github.com/Mico27/SuperMarioBrosMini

or alternatively you can play it here:

https://mico27.itch.io/super-mario-bros-mini

Music and sound files were provided by:
Michirin
Itch.io: https://michirin.itch.io/
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@Michirin9801
